
Reviews::RecordAnswer
  .call
    rolls back if schedule! fails
    with correct answer on first attempt
      creates a ReviewLog
      sets correct and rating on the log
      schedules the card
    with near-miss (typo, one char off)
      assigns Hard rating instead of Again
    with wrong answer (completely different word)
      assigns Again rating
    with multiple attempts (retry)
      correct=false on first attempt means no_recall regardless of attempts count
    with backspace_count and attempts
      saves backspace_count and attempts but does not affect rating
    when called twice on the same card
      creates two ReviewLogs
    word mastery integration (FT-034)
      calls WordMastery::RecordCoverage on correct answer
      does not call WordMastery::RecordCoverage on incorrect answer
      updates UserLexemeState in the same transaction as ReviewLog
      rolls back ReviewLog and contribution if RecordCoverage raises
      creates two ReviewLogs and two contributions when called twice

